		<a href="https://www.niemanlab.org/mobilemajority/"><li class="simple-hubmenu-item hub4" style="color: #BEA234;">Mobile<span class="simple-hubmenu-totrim"> & Apps</span></li></a>
		<a href="https://www.niemanlab.org/hubs/audience-social/"><li class="simple-hubmenu-item hub2" style="color: #43969A;">Audience<span class="simple-hubmenu-totrim"> & Social</span></li></a>
		<a href="https://www.niemanlab.org/hubs/aggregation-discovery/"><li class="simple-hubmenu-item hub1" style="color: #FD860E;">Aggregation<span class="simple-hubmenu-totrim"> & Discovery</span></li></a>
		<a href="https://www.niemanlab.org/hubs/reporting-production/"><li class="simple-hubmenu-item hub5" style="color: #E34D01; border-right: 0;">Reporting<span class="simple-hubmenu-totrim"> & Production</span></li></a>
	</ul>
	<ul class="simple-hubmenu-right">
