<h2 class="simple-headline rejigger">



&#8220;Engaged journalism&#8221; is taking us back to the &#8220;public journalism&#8221; debates of the 1990s</h2>

<div class="simple-post-deck">Plus new research into algorithmic polarization, computational news discovery, gender differences in political news, and more.</div>



 






<div class="simple-bylinerow">

<div class="simple-byline">
<div class="simple-bylineauthor">

<span class="simple-bylineauthor-by">By </span><span class="bylineauthorname"><a href="https://www.niemanlab.org/author/mcoddingtonslewis/" title="Posts by Mark Coddington and Seth Lewis" rel="author">Mark Coddington and Seth Lewis</a></span>




 <span class="simple-bylinedate" style="display: inline; margin-left: 20px; color: #999; text-transform: none; font-weight: normal;">April 3, 2020, 10:45 a.m.</span> <a class="simple-bylineedit" href=""><i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o"></i></a>


</div>  











